@node intr "Short Introduction"

  PowerBattle is a light multiplayer strategygame.  It is not finished
  yet, so things may change every now and then..

  Game is played turn by turn on a hex-based map.  Map is linked from
  edges so that there are no corners.

  @{" !!! IMPORTANT !!! " link impo}
@endnode

