@node unit "Units"

  Each Unit Type has unique definitions.  These will define its
  movement & combat skills, production time, required tech-level etc.

  Two important definitions are: Movement Type & Battle Type.

  Movement Type defines those terrains, where the unit is allowed to
  move (and where NOT).  For example ground units are not allowed to
  move in water.  Air units are allowed to move everywhere.  Biggest
  ships are not allowed to move into lowest waters.

  Battle Type is one of the following:  AIR, GROUND, SEA or SUB.
  Unit's combat abilities are different against these four types.
  There is an extra 'Battle Type' CITY, but it is actually GROUND.

  @{" Introduction of All Unit Types " link utyp}
@endnode



