@node mous "Mouse Controls"

  Left Mouse Button:

  Move or Move To.  Point the target hex where you want to move to,
  and click LMB.  If it is not next to current position, automatic
  MoveTo will be set.

  If there is enemy in target hex, closecombat will be called as
  usual.


  Right Mouse Button:

  RMB has three meanings.

  If under pointer is one of own units, this unit will be selected to
  be commanded.  Units can be sselected from InfoPanels Cargo list or
  Other Units List with RMB as well.

  If target hex is in units' Range, it'll perform ranged attcak if
  possible.

  If target hex is out of unit's Range, next active unit will be
  selected.
@endnode



